Direct Known Subclasses:
CategoryMedia, MediaFile, MediaLibrary, ProgramMedia, StationMedia
public abstract class LibraryObject
extends javax.swing.JComponent

This very simple object provides the basis for all other LibraryObjects (the ProgramMedia, CategoryMedia, MediaFiles, even the MediaLibrary itself) It provides basic logging ability and access to the actual directory or file that this LibraryObject originally came from.

Author:
Carl Angiolillo
